<body>

  <% include ../../partials/header-playground-java.ejs %>

<!-- Tutorial steps -->
<div class="container">

  <p class="mt-3">The <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground</strong> is a cloud-based development environment for Marketing Cloud.
    It has the tools and SDKs you need to create simple apps for Marketing Cloud right within your browser. No need to install anything on your computer!</p>

  <p class="mt-3">We've already created an empty <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground</strong> for you. Let's create a starter <a href="https://maven.apache.org" target="_blank">Apache Maven</a> project in the playground that uses the <a href="http://salesforce-marketingcloud.github.io/FuelSDK-Java/" target="_blank">Marketing Cloud Java SDK</a>.</p>
  
  <!-- Step 1 -->
  <div class="card mt-3">
    <div class="card-block">
      <div class="card-header text-white" style="background-color: #00AA9E;">Create a new Apache Maven project in the playground</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="card-text">Click <strong>Run Command</strong> to create a new Apache Maven project in the playground. </p>
        <pre style="max-height: 30em" data-src="/code-snippets/java/mvn-newproject.sh"></pre>
        <button id="buttonCreateProject" class="btn btn-secondary" type="button">Run command</button>
        <div class="card mt-3">
          <div class="card-header"><small>CONSOLE OUTPUT</small></div>
          <pre style="max-height: 30em" class="m-2">
            <code id="outputCreateProject" class="language-bash">Nothing yet. Click 'Run Command' to see results.</code>
          </pre>
        </div>

        <div id="successCreateProject" class="hide-element">
          <p class="card-text mt-3"><span class="fa fa-star text-success"></span>&nbsp;You have sucessfully created a new Apache Maven project in the playground!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</div>

<div class="container text-center">
  <a class="btn btn-primary btn-md m-4 button-fixed-width-300 active" style="text-align:center" href="/playgrounds/java/java-play-2">Go to step 2</a>
</div>

